Can class inherit the constructor of it's Base class ? 
NO becuase constructor is special method whose name as same as class . ( not satisfy constraint of 
constraictor ) . 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Constructor chaining : 
Constructor chaining is sequence of invoking constructor of same class upon initializing an boject . 
3 para , 2 para  , 1 para , 0 para constrorctor . 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What is Singleton Class ?
A class that can have only one object at time . after first instantation new object also points to 
first instance . 
